Nigerian actress, Annie Idibia, one of Nollywood’s popular actresses, has lost her father to the cold hands of death. The mother of two who is also the wife to famous Nigerian musician, 2face Idibia, took to Instagram to announce the passing of her father. She revealed that the he died after his battle with cancer. She wrote: ‘R I P Daddy. You Fought Hard #cancersucks #thePainIsGone’